{"tid":1491008,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無可能私人檢控黑警施以酷刑？","createTime":"2019-08-20T09:14:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T10:16:41.000Z","uid":27008,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f3b25fac88f25a88c2288a22825db0344360fe1e","tid":1491008,"uid":27008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:14:04.000Z","msg":"根據普通法，每位市民都與律政司有同等權利提出刑事檢控。更重要的是，私人刑事檢控還是監察政府的重要和有力的方法。著名案例Gouriet v Union of Post Office Workers便明確地肯定私人刑事檢控是「針對權力機關怠慢或偏袒的一項寶貴的憲法保障」。本地法律《裁判官條例》第14（1）條亦訂明，任何人都可以按其意願，毋須事先獲得許可，親自或由其代表律師提出刑事檢控。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/denniskwok.wordpress.com/2019/01/09/%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2596%2587%25E7%25AB%25A0%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%25A7%2581%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2588%2591%25E4%25BA%258B%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%258E%25A7/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fdenniskwok.wordpress.com%2F2019%2F01%2F09%2F%2525E3%252580%252590%2525E6%252596%252587%2525E7%2525AB%2525A0%2525E3%252580%252591%2525E7%2525A7%252581%2525E4%2525BA%2525BA%2525E5%252588%252591%2525E4%2525BA%25258B%2525E6%2525AA%2525A2%2525E6%25258E%2525A7%2Famp%2F&d=TRt9Hu9y5T%2Bqj71zgJeH9hmaKe8vvTAxx9uYoYxOzRs%3D&h=e3108754\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/denniskwok.wordpress.com/2019/01/09/%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2596%2587%25E7%25AB%25A0%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%25A7%2581%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2588%2591%25E4%25BA%258B%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%258E%25A7/amp/</a><br />\n<br />\n但成本好似極高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"261caf45f3979af9fc14a068d65cb769b1d6f22f","tid":1491008,"uid":27008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:15:44.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"77d42b6eeaba51afe83cf419a49999d152958e18","tid":1491008,"uid":27008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:15:56.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"fb58bbcd811ec34f59ee14e55762bbd4b71e25ec","tid":1491008,"uid":27008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy